@70013 = ~Wand of Friends~
@70014 = ~This wand will temporarily grant 5 points of Charisma to the wielder. While cast, those who view the wielder tend to be very impressed and will generally make an effort to help <PRO_HIMHER>.

STATISTICS:
(Enchantment/Charm)

Charge abilities:
– Friends
  – Temorarily gain 5 points of Charisma
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: Self
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


